msgctxt "4160_Maya"
msgid "Kiryu-san!?"
msgstr "¡¿Kiryu-san?!"

msgctxt "4172_Player"
msgid "Sorry to keep you waiting."
msgstr "Lamento hacerle esperar."

msgctxt "4184_Maya"
msgid "Who is that with you?"
msgstr "Who is that with you?"

msgctxt "4196_Player"
msgid "I thought it would be just the two of us."
msgstr "I thought it would be just the two of us."

msgctxt "4208_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "4220_Maya"
msgid "I'll wait here. I hope you'll be alone when you get back."
msgstr "I'll wait here. I hope you'll be alone when you get back."

msgctxt "4232_Police Officer"
msgid "Where are you off to today?"
msgstr "¿Adónde vas hoy?"

msgctxt "4244_Maya"
msgid "Hm, I'm not sure yet."
msgstr "Mm, todavía no estoy segura."

msgctxt "4256_Police Officer"
msgid "You waiting for someone? Your boyfriend?"
msgstr "¿Estás esperando a alguien? ¿Como tu novio?"

msgctxt "4268_Maya"
msgid "Oh, something like that."
msgstr "Oh, algo así."

msgctxt "4280_Police Officer"
msgid "Hmm, I see... Thanks for your time, ma'am."
msgstr "Mmm, ya veo... Gracias por su tiempo, señorita."

msgctxt "4292_Maya"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr "Claro."

msgctxt "4316_Player"
msgid "Something wrong?"
msgstr "¿Todo bien?"

msgctxt "4328_Maya"
msgid "Hey, you're late! Where've you been!?"
msgstr "Hey, you're late! Where've you been!?"

msgctxt "4340_Player"
msgid "Sorry."
msgstr "Lo siento."

msgctxt "4352_Maya"
msgid "I'll forgive you this once, but you'll have to make up for it!"
msgstr "I'll forgive you this once, but you'll have to make up for it!"

msgctxt "4364_Player"
msgid "You seem to get questioned by the police a lot."
msgstr "You seem to get questioned by the police a lot."

msgctxt "4376_Maya"
msgid "I'm used to it by now."
msgstr "Ya estoy acostumbrada."

msgctxt "4388_Player"
msgid "That cop was asking some personal questions."
msgstr "Ese policía estaba haciendo algunas preguntas personales."

msgctxt "4400_Maya"
msgid "That's pretty normal. They don't usually go for \"just the facts.\""
msgstr "Es bastante normal. No suelen ir a por \"solo los hechos\"."

msgctxt "4412_Player"
msgid "Yeah, I suppose casually chatting with people puts them more at ease..."
msgstr "Sí, supongo que charlar casualmente con la gente hace que se sientan más a gusto..."

msgctxt "4424_Maya"
msgid "Anyway, what are we doing today?"
msgstr "En fin, ¿qué haremos hoy?"

msgctxt "4436_Player"
msgid "(What should we do?)"
msgstr "(¿Qué deberíamos hacer...?)"

msgctxt "4460_Player"
msgid "(Where should we go...)"
msgstr "(¿A qué lugar deberíamos ir...?)"

msgctxt "4472_Player"
msgid "(Where should we go...)"
msgstr "(¿A qué lugar deberíamos ir...?)"

msgctxt "4484_Player"
msgid "(We could go shopping.)"
msgstr "(¿A dónde deberíamos ir de compras...?)"

msgctxt "4496_Player"
msgid "(We could go out to eat.)"
msgstr "(¿A dónde deberíamos ir a comer...?)"

msgctxt "4520_Player"
msgid "How about Kanrai for some yakiniku?"
msgstr "¿Qué te parece si vamos a Kanrai por un poco de yakiniku?"

msgctxt "4532_Maya"
msgid "I love yakiniku! ♪ I'm pretty hungry, so let's head out \r\n"
"already! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "I love yakiniku! ♪ I'm pretty hungry, so let's head out \r\n"
"already! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

