msgctxt "4568_Maya"
msgid "What, again? We just had that... Going there makes my clothes stink, so I don't really want to go there too often."
msgstr "What, again? We just had that... Going there makes my clothes stink, so I don't really want to go there too often."

msgctxt "4580_Police Officer"
msgid "Well, whatever. C'mon, let's head out."
msgstr "Well, whatever. C'mon, let's head out."

