msgstr "Sí."

msgctxt "4808_Player"
msgid "Hmm, I'm not really in that much of a need of getting new fashionable stuff, but..."
msgstr "Hmm, I'm not really in that much of a need of getting new fashionable stuff, but..."

msgctxt "4844_Player"
msgid "Why don't we go chill and eat light at Watami?"
msgstr "¿Por qué no nos relajamos y vamos a comer algo ligero en Watami?"

msgctxt "4856_Maya"
msgid "I love Watami, too! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default> As long as there's drinks, I can go till morning! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
